Class SecurityDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.events.transport.SecurityDefinition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISecurityPermissionChangeSet

    public final class SecurityDefinition
extends Object
implements ISecurityPermissionChangeSet
    The security information that an Item or an alert feed needs in order to calculate SecurityAccessLevels and SecurityGrantLevels.

    4.0
